{"text": "The power of a lens of focal length of 1 metre is one dioptre.", "fibs": ["power"]}
{"text": "Power of a lens is positive for a converging lens and negative for a diverging lens.", "fibs": ["lens"]}
{"text": "Thus, when an optician prescribes a corrective lens of power + 2.5 D, the required lens is a convex lens of focal length + 40 cm.", "fibs": ["optician"]}
{"text": "A lens of power of – 4.0 D means a concave lens of focal length – 25 cm.", "fibs": ["lens"]}
